                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Chris Gearing &amp;lt;chris@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/a86c75bc-0f85-11e1-aad7-52540025f9af&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/a86c75bc-0f85-11e1-aad7-52540025f9af&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_metabench failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;03/02/2014 12:54:06&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; Leaving par_create_multidir&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;03/02/2014 12:55:55&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; FATAL error on process 0&lt;br/&gt;
Proc 0: Unable to stat file &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;/mnt/lustre/d0.metabench/CREATE_MD_008.000/W.Pet5&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;: No such file or directory&lt;br/&gt;
